import React from 'react'
import '../index.css'


const Login = () => {
  return (
   <>
   <form action="/login" method="post" id='form-data'>
      <label htmlFor="FirstName">Firstname</label>
      <input type="text" name="FirstName" placeholder='firstname' id="firstname" className='input-box' />
      <label htmlFor="lastname">lastname:</label>
      <input type="text" name="lastname" id="name" className='input-box' />
      <label htmlFor="email">email:</label>
      <input type="email" name="email" id="email_input" className='input-box' />
      <label htmlFor="set-password">password:</label>
      <input type="password" name="set-password" className='input-box' id="password" />
      <label htmlFor="confirm-pass">confirm-password:</label>
      <input type="password" name="confirm-pass" className='input-box' id="confirm-password" />
      <button type="submit">Submit</button>
      </form>
   </>
  )
}

export default Login
